  <content contentuid="h84ca7e11g2f56g48bfga1ccgc96f143d4d56" version="1">You learns new ways to deal colossal blows to your enemies. Each can be used once per &lt;LSTag Tooltip="ShortRest"&gt;Short Rest&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>


